snippet.title: Get Out - Reveal Trailer (Co-Op Horror Game)
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2828770/Get_Out/
Join the discord for updates: https://discord.gg/Mg4yURwJ

Get Out is a 1-4 player online co-op psychological horror. Complete tasks and puzzles to banish the entities that have you and your team trapped, and make sure to get out, before they get you.
